{"tid":245558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼女遭鬼父性侵61次還拍片 威脅要像「李宗瑞…不停轉載」","createTime":"2017-05-16T10:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T12:13:38.000Z","uid":1735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb0f452fe05d81e7ee8a8fd3adc4a38cca9f7cc","tid":245558,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"新北市有一名可惡至極的鬼父，他從2012年就開始不斷猥褻、性侵繼女，甚至還揚言要散布不雅影片，要讓她像「李宗瑞案」一樣會不停被轉載，威脅繼女不可以拒絕他的「邀約」，逼她繼續當他發洩的工具，直到去年5月，繼女忍無可忍打給親戚求助，案情才因此曝了光。<br />\n<br />\n根據判決書指出，當時14歲少女在母親離婚後，就在嫁給40多歲目前在押的變態鬼父，他們一家3口原本同住在新北市蘆洲區，可是在2012年9月起，鬼父都會偷偷趁妻子不在家的時候潛入繼女的房間，趁她熟睡之際伸狼爪撫摸胸部和下體，雖然繼女當下有驚醒，但因為心中湧起無限的恐懼，她只好裝睡當不知道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/182907_c552f36a9d8b4ff19a47f6350eab3b4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F182907_c552f36a9d8b4ff19a47f6350eab3b4b.jpg&h=e1a2a323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒想到，繼女的那1次容忍讓鬼父食髓知味，自那之後就多次闖入繼女房間性侵得逞，由於繼女實在太害怕，又擔心自己講出去會讓家庭破碎，只好一直隱忍鬼父的惡行，直到隔年家族母親節聚餐時，她才向舅舅透露父親會觸碰她的身體，讓舅舅驚覺不單純，叫她離家裡和外曾祖母同住。<br />\n<br />\n但誇張的是，即便繼女逃離了鬼窟，鬼父依然不斷糾纏，甚至到學校門口堵人，逼迫繼女如果不乖乖聽話，就要把不雅影片散布到網路上，完全不理會繼女的多次抗拒，還說「真的要逼我PO嗎」、「妳知道有一些東西放到網路上面，人家會不停轉載，像李宗瑞&hellip;」等威脅話語，讓繼女不得拒絕發生關係，並用手機錄下過程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/182922_c5de6546059608e2280bbf85c2e75f25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F182922_c5de6546059608e2280bbf85c2e75f25.jpg&h=a931a46d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直到去年5月，繼女終於忍無可忍，打電話像舅媽哭訴自己長期遭鬼父性侵，協助報案後檢警就在鬼父住處搜出5段不雅影片，向法院聲押獲准至今，新北地院今認定他共猥褻繼女4次、性侵61次，並依強制性交等罪合併判他17年10月徒刑。"},{"pid":"e5d26dfe51320f0884dba3156bc094b848d4759b","tid":245558,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"愛莉是你？"},{"pid":"d45c1eeafc664cc96f9778388c4d65d2d934bca9","tid":245558,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b43dea9b22ef6957c7de03e252b801977edb87","tid":245558,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c22a2fc1db0e67b66ef2310212955bc562c1817","tid":245558,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17074b566bbb9918d63009d91c7c9ee5a910f56b","tid":245558,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4d907cb6869460e24cc06d4443b533a6ec90b8","tid":245558,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58834fcf32dd708f7aa2aa5497e28f919da8069f","tid":245558,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8aad24831c573ceb8054f3e5122416457721a2","tid":245558,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380f7726b883f662a286a3761b3a6f314ef342c7","tid":245558,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:33:23.000Z","msg":"14<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3309328f9667550da729013001063acdf2e76049","tid":245558,"uid":86097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdf464c0e9a4c9efce22ca11c160bc85eb9fbeb5","tid":24